<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,654,1113]" box="[151,888,654,682]" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,654,680]" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">Description.</emphasis>
Body length (including tegmina), male: 6.0– 
<quantity box="[804,884,655,681]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.3" pageId="10" pageNumber="391" unit="mm" value="6.3">6.3mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,654,1113]" box="[199,961,691,717]" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">
Colour as in 
<taxonomicName box="[343,512,691,717]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Hecaloidella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="borneoensis">
<emphasis box="[343,363,691,716]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[377,512,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">borneoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but head marking sometimes indistinct.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,654,1113]" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">
Male genitalia similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[484,654,727,753]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Hecaloidella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="borneoensis">
<emphasis box="[484,504,727,752]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[519,654,727,753]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="391">borneoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but shaft shorter and more evenly curved dorsally to apex and preatrium slightly longer.
</paragraph>
